00:49:12,160 --> 00:49:13,127
This one's good.

614
00:49:13,320 --> 00:49:15,209
- Now you go over there.
- Come here.

615
00:49:15,400 --> 00:49:16,447
Sit here.

616
00:49:18,840 --> 00:49:21,969
