619
00:49:27,080 --> 00:49:29,367
Let's see. Big smile.

620
00:49:29,560 --> 00:49:31,210
Look natural!

621
00:49:34,800 --> 00:49:37,201
- Very good!
- That's it.

622
00:49:48,520 --> 00:49:49,646
Is that from ismael?

623
00:49:51,680 --> 00:49:53,091
He keeps sending me photos.

624
00:49:54,560 --> 00:49:56,050
