677
00:53:55,320 --> 00:53:57,163
We had to ask directions
at one point...

678
00:53:57,360 --> 00:53:57,963
Luis!

679
00:54:02,920 --> 00:54:04,251
You really stirred it up.

680
00:54:04,640 --> 00:54:06,529
- Were you angry?
- A bit.

681
00:54:06,800 --> 00:54:10,521
