725
00:56:52,080 --> 00:56:52,842
Good evening.

726
00:56:53,600 --> 00:56:54,203
Félix,

727
00:56:54,920 --> 00:56:57,161
this is Luis, alika's husband.

728
00:57:02,560 --> 00:57:04,483
